  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/High_Septon\" title=\"High Septon\"><img alt=\"Star of the Faith.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/9/91/Star_of_the_Faith.svg/50px-Star_of_the_Faith.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/9/91/Star_of_the_Faith.svg/75px-Star_of_the_Faith.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/9/91/Star_of_the_Faith.svg/100px-Star_of_the_Faith.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Septon</span><br />Robeson</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/High_Septon\" title=\"High Septon\"><img alt=\"Star of the Faith.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/9/91/Star_of_the_Faith.svg/50px-Star_of_the_Faith.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/9/91/Star_of_the_Faith.svg/75px-Star_of_the_Faith.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/9/91/Star_of_the_Faith.svg/100px-Star_of_the_Faith.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Titles</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Septon\" title=\"Septon\">Septon</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/Regent\" title=\"Regent\">Regent</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/High_Septon\" title=\"High Septon\">High Septon</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/Father_of_the_Faithful\" title=\"Father of the Faithful\">Father of the Faithful</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/His_High_Holiness\" title=\"His High Holiness\">His High Holiness</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/Shepherd_of_the_Faithful\" title=\"Shepherd of the Faithful\">Shepherd of the Faithful</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/Voice_of_the_Seven_on_Earth\" title=\"Voice of the Seven on Earth\">Voice of the Seven on Earth</a></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiances</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Faith_of_the_Seven\" title=\"Faith of the Seven\">Faith of the Seven</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Hightower\" title=\"House Hightower\">House Hightower</a></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Reach\" title=\"Reach\">Reach</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Robeson</b> was a <a href=\"/index.php/Septon\" title=\"Septon\">septon</a> during the rule of Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Damon_Hightower\" title=\"Damon Hightower\">Damon Hightower</a> over <a href=\"/index.php/Oldtown\" title=\"Oldtown\">Oldtown</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Robeson&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>When <a href=\"/index.php/Damon_Hightower\" title=\"Damon Hightower\">Damon Hightower</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_the_Hightower\" title=\"Lord of the Hightower\">Lord of the Hightower</a>, died of a bad belly, Robeson became <a href=\"/index.php/Regent\" title=\"Regent\">regent</a> for Damon's newborn son, <a href=\"/index.php/Triston_Hightower\" title=\"Triston Hightower\">Triston</a>. Robeson ruled Oldtown in all but name for twenty years and ultimately became the first <a href=\"/index.php/High_Septon\" title=\"High Septon\">High Septon</a>. Lord Triston raised the <a href=\"/index.php/Starry_Sept\" title=\"Starry Sept\">Starry Sept</a> in Robeson's honor after his passing.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_reach:_oldtown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf_the_reach:_oldtown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Robeson&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiaf_the_reach:_oldtown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_reach:_oldtown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, The Reach: Oldtown.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<table class=\"wikitable succession-box noprint\" style=\"margin:0.5em auto; font-size:small;clear:both;\">\n\n<tbody><tr>\n<td style=\"width: 30%; text-align: center;\" rowspan=\"1\"><b>New title</b>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 40%; text-align: center;\" rowspan=\"1\"><b>1st<br /> <a href=\"/index.php/High_Septon\" title=\"High Septon\">High Septon</a><br /><a href=\"/index.php/Father_of_the_Faithful\" title=\"Father of the Faithful\">Father of the Faithful</a><br /><a href=\"/index.php/His_High_Holiness\" title=\"His High Holiness\">His High Holiness</a><br /><a href=\"/index.php/Shepherd_of_the_Faithful\" title=\"Shepherd of the Faithf